        {
            "title": "高盛因能源價格影響下調日本東證指數目標",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/96rpNewOLVt7Kw59K1.Ucw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEB6200T_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 高盛週日下調了對日本東證指數的目標,理由是由於中東戰爭持續導致能源價格上漲,預期盈利增長將放緩。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛將東證指數3個月、6個月和12個月目標分別下調至3,800點、4,000點和4,200點,此前目標分別為3,900點、4,100點和4,300點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該投資銀行表示,此次下調是由於預期荷姆茲海峽持續中斷將導致石油和天然氣價格上漲。這是因為美國與以色列對伊朗的戰爭幾乎沒有降溫跡象,週末葉門胡塞武裝襲擊以色列後,戰事可能進入新的前線。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dec71363-86f1-3099-8db2-298826ff349e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛將東證指數2026財年每股盈利增長預估從衝突開始前的12.3%下調至7.2%,假設荷姆茲海峽中斷影響持續六週為基本情境。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該銀行表示,市場情緒仍然脆弱,並補充說,對中東衝突迅速解決的預期已大幅降低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">東證指數在3月份錄得10.2%的跌幅,受到伊朗戰爭爆發的打擊。東證指數的下跌是因為市場預期日本經濟將面臨更多與能源相關的中斷,以及荷姆茲海峽航運活動減少導致的更廣泛供應鏈中斷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月份的跌幅將終結東證指數連續11個月的漲勢——在過去一年中,該指數曾創下一系列歷史新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛指出,以國內市場為主的日本股票仍然表現強勁,保險公司和防禦性股票也是如此。製藥和醫療保健類股在近幾週表現尤為突出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
